Aleksa Palladino https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aleksa_Palladino 0 Aleksa Palladino (born September 21, 1980) is an American actress and singer, perhaps best known for her lead roles in Manny Lo, The Adventures of Sebastian Cole, Find Me Guilty, Boardwalk Empire, Wrong Turn 2: Dead End, and Before the Devil Knows You're Dead.
